This code combines ESP HTTPD and Tuan's MQTT and is intended to trigger external SSR for powering on the heater in my living room.
It's completely manipulated from MQTT and outside logic.

Tuan's MQTT: https://github.com/tuanpmt/esp_mqtt
ESPHTTPD: http://www.esp8266.com/viewtopic.php?f=6&t=376 / http://git.spritesserver.nl/esphttpd.git/
